<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDateOfAmendment" id="idc30a73b8-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date of 1976 Amendment</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Amendment by <ref href="/us/pl/94/581">Pub. L. 94–581</ref> effective <date date="1976-10-21">Oct. 21, 1976</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/94/581/s211">section 211 of Pub. L. 94–581</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t38/s111">section 111 of this title</ref>.</p>
